-- > INGEN INTERNAL CASE FILE #02843-1868 [EUPHOBERIA ARMIGERA] CODENAME: TRAIN >844
A small and narrow myriapod that scoots in the underbrush, eating dead leaves and decaying corpses. A prehistoric cleanup crew, if you will.
